To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private KaufmanEfficiencyRatio _ker;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_ker = KER(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_ker.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "kaufmanefficiencyratio", _ker.Current.Value);
}
